channel.title: A decent bot run
channel.description:
Created my account on the,... 21st I think it was, started botting on the 23rd, now got 75wc and 41 smithing, along with 300k worth of yews. I plan to bot until 80 woodcutting (at willows) and then focus on yews until I have 500k and then start smithing, when I have spent 500k smithing, with enough left over for each type of pickaxe, I will mine until I have level 60 (powermining up until level 40, then mining coal, buying iron and smelting steel, before smithing it)
So yeah, wish me luck :D
